Hi, this is Mariana Li Chen, welcome to my website!
I am currently pursuing my Master of Data Science in Computational Linguistics at the University of British Columbia (UBC). With a passion for uncovering insights through data, I am excited to explore innovative ways to solve real-world challenges using analytics and machine learning. Feel free to browse around and learn more about my journey, projects, and aspirations!
Nice to meet you!
